  lhinv-1.1-r3.ebuild, lhinv-1.1-r4.ebuild:
  Masked lhinv-1.1-r4.ebuild stable for ppc

  05 Oct 2004; Pieter Van den Abeele <pvdabeel@gentoo.org>
  lhinv-1.1-r3.ebuild:
  Masked lhinv-1.1-r3.ebuild stable for ppc

  13 Jul 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> lhinv-1.1-r4.ebuild:
  QA fix in src_unpack. Changed cd ${S} && unpack ${A} || die to what it
  should be. Changed epatch to use ${PN}.

*lhinv-1.1-r4 (11 Jul 2004)

