  Added a sit/vmnet interface type patch. Thanks to Tyler Montbriand
  <tsm@accesscomm.ca> in bug 54344.

  10 Jul 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> lhinv-1.1-r3.ebuild:
  Added ~amd64.

